<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>ResidIA – Gestión de inmuebles para no residentes en España</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;500;600&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --bg-primary: #ffffff;
      --bg-secondary: #f7f6f3;
      --text-primary: #1a1a1a;
      --text-secondary: #6b6b6b;
      --text-tertiary: #aaaaaa;
      --border: rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
      --border-md: rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
      --green-dark: #085041;
      --green-mid: #0F6E56;
      --green-light: #1D9E75;
      --green-pale: #E1F5EE;
      --green-soft: #9FE1CB;
      --amber-pale: #FAEEDA;
      --amber-dark: #633806;
      --amber-mid: #854F0B;
      --blue-pale: #E6F1FB;
      --purple-pale: #EEEDFE;
      --pink-pale: #FBEAF0;
      --leaf-pale: #EAF3DE;
      --radius-md: 8px;
      --radius-lg: 12px;
    }

    body { font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; color: var(--text-primary); background: var(--bg-primary); }

    /* NAV */
    nav {
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 1.2rem 2.5rem;
      border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--border);
      background: var(--bg-primary);
      position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 100;
    }
    .logo { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.3px; }
    .logo span { color: var(--green-light); }
    .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 2rem; font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-secondary); }
    .nav-links a { text-decoration: none; color: inherit; cursor: pointer; }
    .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--text-primary); }
    .nav-cta {
      font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500;
      padding: 8px 20px;
      border: 0.5px solid var(--border-md);
      border-radius: var(--radius-md);
      cursor: pointer;
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--text-primary);
      transition: background 0.15s;
    }
    .nav-cta:hover { background: var(--bg-secondary); }

    /* HERO */
    .hero-wrap { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .hero {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 3rem; align-items: center;
      padding: 5rem 2.5rem 4rem;
    }
    .hero-tag {
      display: inline-block; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 1.5px;
      text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--green-mid);
      background: var(--green-pale); padding: 5px 12px;
      border-radius: var(--radius-md); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    .hero h1 {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 44px; line-height: 1.2; font-weight: 500;
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    }
    .hero h1 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--green-light); }
    .hero p { font-size: 16px; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    .cta-row { display: flex; gap: 12px; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .btn-primary {
      padding: 12px 28px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500;
      background: var(--green-dark); color: var(--green-pale);
      border: none; border-radius: var(--radius-md); cursor: pointer;
      transition: opacity 0.15s;
    }
    .btn-primary:hover { opacity: 0.85; }
    .btn-secondary {
      padding: 12px 28px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500;
      background: transparent; color: var(--text-primary);
      border: 0.5px solid var(--border-md);
      border-radius: var(--radius-md); cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 0.15s;
    }
    .btn-secondary:hover { background: var(--bg-secondary); }
    .hero-trust { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-tertiary); margin-top: 1.5rem; }

    /* HERO VISUAL */
    .hero-visual {
      background: var(--bg-secondary);
      border: 0.5px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }
    .dash-header { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
    .dash-title { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; }
    .dash-badge { font-size: 11px; background: var(--green-pale); color: var(--green-mid); padding: 3px 10px; border-radius: 20px; }
    .stat-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .stat-card {
      background: var(--bg-primary);
      border: 0.5px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius-md); padding: 12px 14px;
    }
    .stat-label { font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .stat-val { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 500; }
    .stat-sub { font-size: 11px; color: var(--green-light); margin-top: 2px; }
    .prop-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; }
    .prop-item {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
      background: var(--bg-primary);
      border: 0.5px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius-md); padding: 10px 12px;
    }
    .prop-icon {
      width: 32px; height: 32px; border-radius: 6px;
      background: var(--green-soft); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 14px; flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .prop-name { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; }
    .prop-loc { font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-secondary); }
    .prop-status { margin-left: auto; font-size: 11px; padding: 3px 8px; border-radius: 20px; }
    .status-ok { background: var(--green-pale); color: var(--green-mid); }
    .status-warn { background: var(--amber-pale); color: var(--amber-mid); }
    .alert-bar {
      margin-top: 10px; padding: 10px 12px;
      background: var(--amber-pale); border-radius: var(--radius-md);
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
      font-size: 12px; color: var(--amber-dark);
    }

    /* FLAGS */
    .flags {
      display: flex; gap: 6px; padding: 1.5rem 2.5rem;
      border-top: 0.5px solid var(--border);
      border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--border);
      background: var(--bg-secondary);
      font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-secondary);
      overflow-x: auto;
    }
    .flag-intro { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-tertiary); margin-right: 4px; white-space: nowrap; align-self: center; }
    .flag-item {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; white-space: nowrap;
      padding: 4px 12px; background: var(--bg-primary);
      border-radius: 20px; border: 0.5px solid var(--border);
    }

    /* FEATURES */
    .features { padding: 4rem 2.5rem; max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .section-label { font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--green-light); font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
    .section-title { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 32px; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
    .section-sub { font-size: 15px; color: var(--text-secondary); max-width: 500px; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 3rem; }

    .feat-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1.5rem; }
    .feat-card {
      border: 0.5px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: 1.5rem;
      background: var(--bg-primary);
      transition: border-color 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    }
    .feat-card:hover { border-color: var(--border-md); box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.06); }
    .feat-icon {
      width: 40px; height: 40px; border-radius: 10px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .feat-title { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .feat-desc { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.6; }
    .feat-chips { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 5px; margin-top: 10px; }
    .chip { font-size: 11px; padding: 3px 8px; border-radius: 20px; border: 0.5px solid var(--border); color: var(--text-secondary); }

    /* TAX SECTION */
    .tax-section { background: var(--bg-secondary); padding: 4rem 2.5rem; }
    .tax-inner { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 3rem; align-items: center; }
    .tax-steps { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; }
    .tax-step {
      display: flex; gap: 14px; align-items: flex-start;
      padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
      background: var(--bg-primary);
      border-radius: var(--radius-md);
      border: 0.5px solid var(--border);
    }
    .step-num {
      width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--green-dark); color: var(--green-soft);
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 12px; font-weight: 500; flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .step-title { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 2px; }
    .step-desc { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.5; }

    /* PRICING */
    .pricing { padding: 4rem 2.5rem; max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center; }
    .price-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 1.25rem; text-align: left; }
    .price-card {
      border: 0.5px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: 1.5rem;
      background: var(--bg-primary);
    }
    .price-card.featured { border: 2px solid var(--green-light); }
    .price-badge {
      font-size: 11px; background: var(--green-pale); color: var(--green-mid);
      padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 20px; display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .price-name { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .price-val { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 32px; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }
    .price-period { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
    .price-feats { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 7px; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
    .pf { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-secondary); display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: baseline; }
    .pf::before { content: '–'; color: var(--green-light); flex-shrink: 0; }
    .price-btn {
      width: 100%; padding: 10px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500;
      border-radius: var(--radius-md); cursor: pointer;
      border: 0.5px solid var(--border-md);
      background: transparent; color: var(--text-primary);
      transition: background 0.15s;
    }
    .price-btn:hover { background: var(--bg-secondary); }
    .price-btn.green { background: var(--green-dark); color: var(--green-pale); border: none; }
    .price-btn.green:hover { opacity: 0.85; }

    /* FOOTER */
    footer {
      border-top: 0.5px solid var(--border);
      padding: 2rem 2.5rem;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
      background: var(--bg-primary);
      font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-secondary);
      flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 1rem;
    }
    .footer-logo { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 500; }
    .footer-logo span { color: var(--green-light); }
    .footer-links { display: flex; gap: 1.5rem; }
    .footer-links a { text-decoration: none; color: inherit; cursor: pointer; }
    .footer-links a:hover { color: var(--text-primary); }

    /* RESPONSIVE */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .hero { grid-template-columns: 1fr; padding: 3rem 1.5rem; }
      .feat-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .tax-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .price-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      nav { padding: 1rem 1.5rem; }
      .nav-links { display: none; }
      .flags { padding: 1rem 1.5rem; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- NAV -->
  <nav>
    <div class="logo">Resid<span>IA</span></div>
    <div class="nav-links">
      <a href="#funcionalidades">Funcionalidades</a>
      <a href="#impuestos">Impuestos</a>
      <a href="#precios">Precios</a>
      <a href="#contacto">Ayuda</a>
    </div>
    <button class="nav-cta">Ver demo</button>
  </nav>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <div class="hero-wrap">
    <div class="hero">
      <div>
        <div class="hero-tag">Para no residentes en España</div>
        <h1>Tu patrimonio en España, <em>bajo control</em> desde cualquier país</h1>
        <p>Gestiona tus inmuebles, cumple tus obligaciones tributarias y mantén toda la documentación en orden — sin necesidad de estar físicamente en España.</p>
        <div class="cta-row">
          <button class="btn-primary">Empezar gratis</button>
          <button class="btn-secondary">Ver cómo funciona</button>
        </div>
        <p class="hero-trust">Sin permanencia · Soporte en español, inglés y alemán</p>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-visual">
        <div class="dash-header">
          <span class="dash-title">Mi cartera</span>
          <span class="dash-badge">3 inmuebles</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-grid">
          <div class="stat-card">
            <div class="stat-label">Renta anual</div>
            <div class="stat-val">18.400 €</div>
            <div class="stat-sub">+8% vs año anterior</div>
